document_data.mainbody: Yi Woos Clinic was a healing center located in the Xiousing district in Marsember. It was run by the Shou healer known as Yi Woo. The clinic would treat anyone, Shou or Cormyrean, regardless of ability to pay.Dan Anderson. "Backdrop Xiousing." Dungeon #195. Renton, WA Wizards of the Coast, October 2011.
